Version 0.3.1
-------------

- Player colors are configurable

- When won, the 4 aligned balls rotate

- When playing, AI name rotates

- AI forces have names (beginner, strong, ..)

- Statistic page with the number of games won for each player name and AI force, never reseted.

- Android support


Version 0.2.1
-------------

- Cover is a board object instead of image grabbed: no more memory leaks, and more fun !

- Support for Tablet

- Background can be transparent (configure options) ; still blue by default

- Apropos page added

- License updated to GPLv3

